# Background Reviewer

Multi-LLM parallel code review with named reviewers.

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Determine review scope and round number
# 2. Create: .context/reviews/
# 3. Launch named reviewers in background
# 4. Each reviewer saves findings to {round}-{name}.md
# 5. Merge into prioritized findings when ready
```

## Output Convention

```
.context/reviews/
{{- range .agentsOpencode.roles.reviewer }}
├── R01-{{ .name }}.md    # {{ .for }}
{{- end }}
├── R01-merged.md               # Round 1: merged findings
└── R02-merged.md
```

Detect next round:
```bash
mkdir -p .context/reviews
ROUND=$(printf "R%02d" $(( $(ls .context/reviews/R*-*.md 2>/dev/null | sed 's/.*\/R\([0-9]*\)-.*/\1/' | sort -rn | head -1 | sed 's/^0*//') + 1 )))
```

